title: Stevie Nicks - The Best of Stevie Nicks [2010]
description:
Stevie Nicks - The Best of Stevie Nicks [2010] DVD Rip

If you want a collection of the best songs of Stevie Nicks from both solo career and her glory days with Fleetwood Mac, then you will have to put it together yourself (which, of course, is not that much of a problem in these modern times). If you are looking for the best songs of her solo career then you might as well save yourself the effort and just pick up THIS VIDEO! These video tracks provide ample proof that when she is good, Stevie Nicks is very good.
